text:
Nice place

No shop for 3 pm coffee

This facility is big and famous within industry so it was a reputable yard and need professional security to manage at front gate .. it seems that the processs took very long, not professional at all with long que when they can expedite their security protocol effectively without affecting the clients especially when management team is arriving from oversea ...

One of the Best Shipyard I have Ever seen,
Clean, neat Organized.  And all the jobs are carried out with safe and efficient  manner.
